---
import { Phone, LeafIcon as Liver, Droplets, Route, MapPin } from "@lucide/astro";
---
<section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-white">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto p-8">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-16 h-16 bg-pink-100 rounded-full mb-6">
        <Liver class="w-8 h-8 text-pink-600" />
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">
        ¿Qué evalúa la ecografía hepatobiliar?
      </h2>

      <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        Nuestro estudio examina detalladamente cada estructura para brindarte un
        diagnóstico completo y preciso
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6 mb-16 items-stretch">
      <!-- Hígado -->
      <div
        class="group bg-white p-8 rounded-3xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100 hover:shadow-lg hover:border-pink-200 transition-all duration-300 h-full flex flex-col"
      >
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-pink-500 to-pink-600 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
          <Liver class="w-8 h-8 text-white" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 text-lg">Hígado</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
          Tamaño, contorno, brillo del tejido (ecogenicidad) y presencia de
          lesiones focales (quistes, masas o calcificaciones).
        </p>
        <div class="mt-auto pt-4 border-t border-gray-100">
          <span class="text-xs text-pink-600 font-medium">Evaluación completa</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Vesícula biliar -->
      <div
        class="group bg-white p-8 rounded-3xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100 hover:shadow-lg hover:border-pink-200 transition-all duration-300 h-full flex flex-col"
      >
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-pink-500 to-pink-600 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
          <Droplets class="w-8 h-8 text-white" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 text-lg">Vesícula biliar</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
          Grosor de la pared, contenido (bilis, lodo, pólipos, cálculos) y
          respuesta al palpar con el transductor.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-auto pt-4 border-t border-gray-100">
          <span class="text-xs text-pink-600 font-medium">Análisis detallado</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Vías biliares -->
      <div
        class="group bg-white p-8 rounded-3xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100 hover:shadow-lg hover:border-pink-200 transition-all duration-300 h-full flex flex-col"
      >
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-pink-500 to-pink-600 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
          <Route class="w-8 h-8 text-white" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 text-lg">Vías biliares</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
          Calibre del colédoco y dilataciones que sugieran obstrucción.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-auto pt-4 border-t border-gray-100">
          <span class="text-xs text-pink-600 font-medium">Revisión especializada</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Entorno cercano -->
      <div
        class="group bg-white p-8 rounded-3xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100 hover:shadow-lg hover:border-pink-200 transition-all duration-300 h-full flex flex-col"
      >
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-pink-500 to-pink-600 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
          <MapPin class="w-8 h-8 text-white" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 text-lg">Entorno cercano</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
          Hallazgos alrededor (líquido libre, cambios inflamatorios) que ayuden
          a dar contexto.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-auto pt-4 border-t border-gray-100">
          <span class="text-xs text-pink-600 font-medium">Contexto integral</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-gray-50 to-pink-50 rounded-3xl p-8 md:p-12 mb-12">
      <div class="text-center">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Evaluación integral en una sola sesión</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Nuestros especialistas examinan cada detalle para proporcionarte la
          información más completa sobre tu salud hepática
        </p>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-pink-600 mb-1">4</div>
            <div class="text-sm text-gray-600">Áreas evaluadas</div>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-pink-600 mb-1">100%</div>
            <div class="text-sm text-gray-600">Sin radiación</div>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-pink-600 mb-1">30min</div>
            <div class="text-sm text-gray-600">Duración máx.</div>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-pink-600 mb-1">2</div>
            <div class="text-sm text-gray-600">Radiólogos</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="text-center">
      <a
        href="/hacer-cita"
        class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 bg-pink-600 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-full font-semibold hover:bg-pink-700 transition-all duration-300 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transform hover:-translate-y-1"
      >
        <Phone class="w-5 h-5" />
        Agenda tu Cita
    </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
